Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A racing second hand,\Na broken communication!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.16,0:00:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan's logic works great on\Nhearts tired by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already ski season!\NBe wary of chilly crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid but\Nhas the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ski Lodge Murder Case (Part 1).
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:02:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter! And snow-covered\Nmountains mean skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my long-awaited boy-hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, there's only\Nfive or six guys on the slopes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're all with their girlfriends...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the place really is empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only untaken guy here is Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay,\Nlet's just have fun skiing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay for you \Nsince you have Shinichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried my hardest\Nthese past seventeen years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing good\Nhas ever happened to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you can pay for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kittens!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to ski with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kittens?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ski instructors. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that Mori-{\i1}san {\i0}and Suzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is you! Good to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You know these girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! They were students of mine\Nwhen I taught at Teitan Elementary!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I remember\Na teacher like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you two sure have grown womanly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, you're as stunning as\Never with that long hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just my hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:28.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonehara Akiko - (Ran and Sonoko's former teacher)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Says the thirty year old woman\Nwho could never get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what about these\Nnice instructor friends of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instructors, indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Grade school teachers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you both work with\NYonehara-{\i1}sensei {\i0}at Haido Elementary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! They're my coworkers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher for Class 5-1,\NShimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and boys P.E. instructor,\NSakai-{\i1}sensei{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, grade school teachers trying\Nto pick up high school girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are still so young at heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody uses "kittens" nowadays!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he be? \NSugiyama-{\i1}sensei {\i0}sure is late...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A music teacher\Nwho wound up coming, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We agreed to meet\Nhere at 2:00, but he's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose he went on\Nahead to the lodge we're staying at
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he can scare us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very possible.\NHe loves that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to\Ncome to the lodge, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! No seducing my students!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! We'll drive 'em back\Nin time for their ski bus home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you sure this is the road?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me! Are there\Nany lodges around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's one\Nhalfway up that mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't tell me\Nyou're goin' up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This area gets pounded\Nby blizzards every evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn back while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei \N{\i0}might be waiting for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! Who booked us\Nout here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I thought you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me. Wasn't it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, was it Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:44.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Annual Secret Ski Tour
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just did what that card I found in\Nmy desk two weeks ago said to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and circled that I would attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You usually organize our trips,\Nso I thought you did this one, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Plus, there was another\Nnote in my desk yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A list of the attendees and a map\Nto the meeting place and lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got one, too!\NWho could've put them there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the person\Nwith the key to the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone here must have gotten\Nit from the lodge's owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the key. I found it\Nin my desk yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who rented the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me. Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei \N{\i0}called me last night
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and told me to get a rental car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, wasn't he the\None who planned all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, what're you doing?\NLet's go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was cold out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! A fireplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad we came, Ran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think we\Ncan leave in this blizzard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:07:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll phone your parents,\Nso stay here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, is it really OK\Nto rent such a fancy lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei {\i0}pay,\Nsince he planned this tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's our sponsor, Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming, coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for taking so long, \NSugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a newshound who these folks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:37.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Atsushi (37) - Newspaper Reporter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,really helped out three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a tip-off that something's\Ngonna happen here tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...gonna happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I parked in the forest and waited\Nfor you when a blizzard suddenly hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that wise? I'll just write,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Haido Elementary Teacher\NThrows Reporter Out Into Blizzard."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are\NYonehara-{\i1}sensei {\i0}and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno. Everyone\Nsuddenly stopped talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we were having so much fun.\NThat guy ruined it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about him and\Nhelp me make everyone's beds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you two can help \NNakamura-{\i1}sensei {\i0}with dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, has Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei\N{\i0}called or anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I got his machine at home,\Nso I think he's on his way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nakamura-{\i1}sensei {\i0}isn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anything wrong, Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher! Say something, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mi"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko! What's going on?! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in there, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:09:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonehara-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the commotion here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Someone attacked you?! Honestly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone covered my mouth from\Nbehind while I was making the bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I felt faint...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it this handkerchief?\NPeople on TV do it a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,knocking someone out with a\Nhandkerchief soaked in chloroform.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what's the rope for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was strangled with\Nit after she was knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? There are\Nrope marks on her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no question about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you strangled, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put up a fight, but I don't know\Nwhat happened after I passed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I even had my\Nhead bashed into the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mi"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is lipstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me my...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My lipstick is gone! I had it in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There's some\Non Sonoko's hand, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one says, "Na..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mi" and "na"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mi-na-go-ro-shi." (massacre)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A massacre?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the culprit\Nis trying to tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing nobody died, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you won't have to bend\Nthe truth like you did three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!\NAre you still stuck on that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I bet you attacked them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in front of the fireplace\Nwhen that girl screamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, is it really a good idea\Nto have a brat chase the culprit alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect! There are still tracks here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I follow these...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The front door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That means the attacker...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have inhaled\Ntoo much chloroform.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll wake up soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, was the stuff\Nabout the footprints true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They went from\Nthe window to the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who says\Nthe attacker made them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-{\i1}neechan {\i0}kicked the door\Ndown 'cause it was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That door only locks from the inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the window was the only way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the attacker might've\Ntaken refuge inside the lodge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just \NSugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}'s doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so!\NThat jerk did all this to scare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:13:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get serious! Myself aside,\NSuzuki-{\i1}san {\i0}has been strangled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much to be a prank!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, what could\NSugiyama-{\i1}sensei {\i0}be thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only he'd show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he can't come\Nout now that it's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you when there\Nwere two women being attacked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me. I was takin' a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in my room listening\Nto music on my headphones!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you watch Suzuki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she gets attacked again,\Nbust out your karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamura-{\i1}sensei{\i0}'s shoes are wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Nakamura-{\i1}sensei{\i0}.\N Where were you earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't in the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the gas wasn't coming out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I went out the back\Nto check the gas tanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, where's dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a little more.\NIt's cooking right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smells like curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish making the beds until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go check on dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Planning to filch some food, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for making me some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. There was\Nan extra helping, anyways...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'll never forget what\Nhappened three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what's this "three years ago" stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry about it, little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Those two didn't eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said they'll eat when\NSonoko-{\i1}chan {\i0}wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. We sure have\Ninconvenienced her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Sugiyama!\NWe know you're in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit sneaking around\Nand get out-- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:15:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We're all right.\NThe heater's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the lodge's owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was snowing, so he was worried\Nif the heater was working or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How odd. There's definitely\Nsomething going on in this lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll need to investigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, is the incident three years\Nago everybody's tight-lipped about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, little boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm sure I brought it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The professor's Earring Cell Phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, the professor's number is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? An incident at Haido\NElementary three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be case files\Nin my dad's study!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry! I got a\Nbad feeling about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry,\Nsomeone else might--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was you, Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.39,0:16:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The music teacher has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're ya doin'?\NCome inside already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's wrong?!\NSugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. He's passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he froze to death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See this rope mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, the body's stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that called rigor mortis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though that means he was\Nkilled over nine hours ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that his body rang the\Nbell means someone set him there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, we were all eating\Nby the fireplace when it rang...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the killer isn't one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably the one who attacked\NYonehara-{\i1}sensei {\i0}and Sonoko-{\i1}neechan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the "ko" on his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a letter written\Nin lipstick just like they did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonehara-{\i1}sensei {\i0}had "mi" and\NSonoko-{\i1}neechan {\i0}had "na", which makes:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mi-na-ko."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Shimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got nothing to do with it! Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!\NIt's Yonehara! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait until he cools down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone was murdered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we found Sugiyama-{\i1}sensei{\i0}'s\Nbody leaning by the front door...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They could've snuck inside while\Nwe were all gathered at the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Sakai-{\i1}sensei {\i0}is\Ncalling the police as we speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it's too dangerous\Nto send cars in the blizzard,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we gotta wait until it\Ndies down in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, they want us to sit\Nhere until morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the killer could still be inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did all this have to happen?\NIt was such a fun ski tour...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.26,0:18:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only he were here now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Shinichi! Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who found\Neveryone's lunch money
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I lost it in 4th grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that cheeky runt from the class\Nnext door who acted like a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for being cheeky...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a high school detective now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I did see him\Nin the papers. I think his name was--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kudo Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A brilliant sixteen year old detective\Nwho handled unsolvable cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was pretty good for a kid,\Nso I was gonna do a feature on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's been no word on him lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it he croaked after\Npoking his nose into some case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! Shinichi is ali--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came to warn you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to not take your eyes off that\Nguy holed up in his room upstairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my reporter's instinct\Nis right, he'll be next to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:20:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the more casualties, the better\Nthe article and the better for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right. The upstairs\Nwindows don't open,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he won't get\Nattacked if he's holed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, he is a bit agitated.\NIt's dangerous to leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give him some coffee to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamura-{\i1}sensei {\i0}and I will\Nmake some, so you go be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be extra careful!\NThe killer could be hiding inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dead! I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's gonna kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}! \NCoffee and cocoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where's that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wasn't he with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An outside job... Or was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the doorbell rang, everyone was\Ntogether but Ran and Sonoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it was definitely someone\Nelse who placed the body here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Only that part of\Nthe railing is missing snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone get on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that groove?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one on the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this have been--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you shouldn't wander around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your room and get in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimoda-{\i1}sensei {\i0}won't let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's leave him alone,\Nlock our rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get some rest until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Professor. Figure anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I finally found the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago, a girl hanged\Nherself in the volleyball room
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at Haido Elementary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems the cause was "exam neurosis."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the blame\Nwas focused on her teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the teacher's name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not listed here,\Nbut the girl's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haido Elementary,\NClass 6-2, Mochizuki Minako.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it mention anything else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing there,\NConan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's the professor.\NIs this a phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Shinichi there, Professor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Ran-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upstairs... Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shimoda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.46,0:24:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here! Not here! Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not hidden anywhere,\Nthat means the killer still has the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.12,0:24:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer... is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.20,0:24:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan:\N"The Ski Lodge Murder Case (Part 2)."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.24,0:24:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.48,0:24:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.46,0:24:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode is this year's last episode of Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.01,0:24:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's Christmas, New Year's—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.45,0:24:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you identified the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.53,0:24:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes, I'm screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.75,0:24:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
